title: installation failed on redhat 5.7
body_html:
I installed tf from source code on redhat 5.7(I know it is a very old version), when I try to import tensorflow, it gives: anaconda/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tensorflow/python/_pywrap_tensorflow.so: ELF file OS ABI invalid
How can I solve that?
